        <li><strong>Annual Allowance:</strong> Ongoing deductions each year</li>
        <li><strong>Interest Deduction:</strong> Loan interest is 100% deductible</li>
      </ul>

      <p>These deductions lower your taxable income. Lower taxable income means less tax to pay.</p>

